  "title": "Delicate Norwegian Meat Stew",
  "description": "A traditional Norwegian dish featuring tender meat and sweet jam, simmered to perfection in a kazan cauldron, suitable for kids and diabetic-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
